{
  "stem": "17606.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Alec, Eichman, Alec, Mandel, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Landau.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That's all what I remember at the moment.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Maybe I'll come back to it [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I'll refresh my memory.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That was, again, a double success for us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We deceived the German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We saved some 60 some Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And-- and first of all, they deceived the German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they got rid of some Jewish gestapo men.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That was still action of the civil disobedience group.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Then later on, the civil disobedience group was changed to [NON-ENGLISH], avengers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Then we were selecting our own gestapo men and liquidate them as much we could.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Occasionally, we beat them up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And in most cases, we just eliminated them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The first big action started July 22 of 1942.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'll come to it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Officially, they were transported to a to work in the fields and to work in industry and better surroundings than-- in Warsaw to work in shops.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was the official excuse.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As the work progressed, they were giving out two loaves of bread to volunteers and 2 kilo of marmalade.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And many hungry people came just to get the two loaves of bread and went to, so-called, [INAUDIBLE] or Trawniki, where they were supposed to work in [INAUDIBLE] and shops.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And like I said, there's the president of the Judenrat committed suicide.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But [INAUDIBLE] was going out till September, almost till September of 1942.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "At the end, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] before the end of this, two man came to Warsaw whom I knew personally, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They contact me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then I took him to the Doctor-- Dr.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "David [INAUDIBLE], who wrote the book I have that book.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He mention me a few times in the book.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
